                  <li><b>Unusual Noises: </b>Strange sounds coming from your wine cooler or wine fridge, such as buzzing, clicking, or humming, can indicate issues with the evaporator coils or the entire system.</li>
                  <li><b>Frost Build-Up: </b>If you notice frost or ice accumulation on the evaporator coils, this could signal a problem with the cooling system that needs immediate attention.</li>
